author: Andrew Phillip Kennedy
text:
At this point just throw the whole damn country away and start over from scratch. 

It’s absolutely insane to me that 9 old ass people sitting on the highest court in the land can ban something that 70 fucking % of the American people support.

author: Andrew Phillip Kennedy
text:
The Rs have poisoned & destroyed every branch of government, what little faith the people had in it, and have forced their will, their beliefs, and what freedoms THEY think people should have on everyone else.

And it’s bullshit.

text: I don’t even have the words today. They make it really fucking hard to love this country.
